\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domitia\">Domitia\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Chimen\n                    na\">Chimen-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>na\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aulo\">A(ulo)\u003C/span> · \u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aemilio\">Aemilio\u003C/span> · \u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aristomeni\">Aristomeni\u003C/span> · et · suis \u003Cbr id=\"al4-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>h(oc) · m(onumentum) · \u003Cbr id=\"al5-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>h(eredem) · n(on) · s(equetur) \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Domitia\">DOMITIA\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Chimen\n                    na\">CHIMEN\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>NA\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aulo\">A\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aemilio\">AEMILIO\u003C/span>·\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aristomeni\">ARISTOMENI\u003C/span>·ET·SUIS\u003Cbr id=\"al4-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">4\u003C/span>H·M·\u003Cbr id=\"al5-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">5\u003C/span>H·N·S\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000579_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic000579_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000579.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic000579-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>CIL\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Domitia Chimenna for Aulus Aemilius Aristomenus and his children. This monument does not pass to the heir.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Korhonen makes a convincing case that the text is originally from Termini, not an importation from Rome; he also notes the unusual name, attested also in CIL 10.7394, with suffix similar to other Greek examples, and perhaps a Sikel onomastic example (noting that linguistic interference is rare in the Termini Latin inscriptions).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Gualtherus 1624 89 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] 249 \u0